data.description: New Roof, Freshly Painted. Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 full bath and 2 car garage with lots of amenities. This home has a long cover porch, beautiful arches leading into huge living room with ceiling, open to the kitchen, microwave, lots of cabin space, breakfast bar, and eat in kitchen.  The office room / formal dining with double french doors at in the entry, two of bedroom have walk-in closet, ceiling fans, gorgeous private master bedroom, long walk-in closet, garden tub, double vanities, back yard with extended concrete on the back and side, cover patio, storage shed and a wood privacy fence.
